title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 4 2021
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Aug 4 2021
description:
PODCAST SUMMARY HOUR 2: Senator Ron Johnson talks to C&B about covid, infrastructure, January 6th, the Chinese threat. Takeaways from the Senator Johnson interview. Is there a Dem civil war brewing over vaccine passports? Boston's mayor says vaccine passports are discriminatory. Many black New Yorkers will be barred under NYC's vaccine passport. DeSantis: Stop judging people who get covid.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
